<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Discovery Ridge</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Discovery Ridge attracts an eclectic mix of white-collar estate owners to mountain bikers and hikers wanting that “Canmore” feel right in the city.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Whether you’re after wilderness, whimsy or proximity to the core, you’ll find it here in Discovery Ridge.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Discovery Ridge has a bevy of dining options including high-end eateries and quaint wine bistros. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">It's not hard to relax in Discovery Ridge, this unique part of Calgary it offers everything from wining and dining to hiking and wilderness biking.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Living in Discovery Ridge can give residents the best of both worlds in terms of amenities and a peaceful lifestyle.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Griffith Woods Environmental Park occupies a large part of the southern border of Discovery Ridge. Huge green lung spaces and scenic views make this community a much-desired location to live in.</p>

        </div>
